        "The card focuses narrowly on DNN performance, but the paper is broader in scope, comparing multiple machine learning regressors (XGBoost, lightGBM, CatBoost, DKL, blending ensemble) and also proposing a meta-learning approach for projection between chromatographic methods.",
        "The card does not mention the meta-learning projection method, which is a significant contribution of the paper alongside the DNN retention time prediction.",
        "The card does not capture the full workflow described in the paper (Fig. 2), which integrates RT prediction with metabolite annotation using mass and RT filtering."
      ],
