    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/10_1186_s13321_022_00613_8__task_004/scope_drift",
      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The card focuses narrowly on the meta-learning projection task with 10-molecule calibration, which is a secondary contribution in the paper. The paper's primary focus is on retention time prediction using various ML regressors (DNN, XGBoost, etc.) on the SMRT dataset, with meta-learning projection as a downstream application.",
        "The card does not mention the primary retention time prediction models (DNN, XGBoost, lightGBM, CatBoost, DKL) that are central to the paper's methodology, only the projection step.",
        "The card omits the METLIN SMRT dataset (80,038 molecules) which is fundamental to the work, and does not mention the HMDB database used for ranking annotations."
      ],
      "asbval:n_drift_notes": 3,
