    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/chromatographic-method-transfer/005",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "GPs are particularly suited as projection model: they represent a distribution over functions, they can perform regression on smalls amount of data, and they can incorporate prior knowledge using the Bayesian framework... Hence, we shall consider: f(\u00b7) ~ GP(...). The outline of the approach is shown in Fig. 4.",
      "asbval:note": "Supported. Paper describes GP-based meta-learning for projection, which would be implemented in the cmmrt repository.",
