    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/chromatographic-method-transfer/008",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Since laboratories usually customize the Chromatographic Method (CM) for the needs of each experiment, a SMRT-based model cannot be directly applied to experimental data from other laboratories, or even other experiments conducted in the same laboratory.",
