      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "5, 666 molecular descriptors and 2, 214 fingerprints (MACCS166, Extended Connectivity, and Path Fingerprints fingerprints) were generated with the alvaDesc software... alvaDesc permits the computation of MACCS166 fingerprints, Extended Connectivity Fingerprints (ECFP) [31] and Path Fingerprints (PFP), making a total of 2, 214 fingerprints. Additionally, the 5, 666 molecular descriptors supported by alvaDesc were also generated",
