    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/molecular-descriptor-fingerprint-generation/004",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Our results slightly favor the usage of fingerprints, although it cannot be ruled out that the best type of feature depends on the machine learning regressor used.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper states fingerprints slightly favor over descriptors but does not definitively show fingerprints achieve lower MAE than descriptors alone across all models. The evidence is more nuanced: 'Preliminary results suggested that using fingerprints, descriptors, and fingerprints+descriptors yielded similar results' (passage 6). The claim overstates the empirical advantage.",
