      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The models included deep neural networks, deep kernel learning, several gradient boosting models, and a blending approach... Bayesian hyperparameter search was used for parameter tuning... To project retention times between chromatographic methods, a novel Bayesian meta-learning approach that can learn from just a few molecules is proposed.",
